Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:18.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到这股心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:22.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上双眼用心去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,满溢的热气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:33.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那一日的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:49.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,苏醒的追忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,katharsis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:57.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,解放吧 将一切解放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着未来跑动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,名为青涩和你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻就传达到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,强而有力地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:14.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝那倾洒而出的光芒 伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:21.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,So Just Light Bravest Destiny
